        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You release an omnidirectional telekinetic burst. Each creature within 20 feet must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes 8d6 force damage and is pushed back 5 feet. On a successful save, a creature takes half damage and isn\u2019t pushed.</p>\n<p>All small objects that are not worn or carried are also pushed 5 feet back.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Force Potency.</strong></em>&nbsp;When you cast this power using a force slot of 4th level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 3rd.</p>",
